    Extended Program Check

    Complete check of the ABAP source text for all statically recognizable errors. Programs with errors in the extended program check can be executed, but usually result in an excdeption. Call in the ABAP Editor via Program → Check → Extended Program Check or via transaction code SLIN.

    7.31 7.40 7.54

    ABAP Keyword Documentation →  ABAP Glossary
